SVPN is a  company that provides personal  privacy and security services for individuals from over 120 countries.

In May 1999 SVPN created its first secure, encrypted internet network to protect the identity of individuals and prevent eavesdropping of Internet communications, in January 2012 a new version that further enhances anonymity and gives users more privacy control moved into private beta.  

The new SVPN privacy system designed to prevent blocking will become generally available for public beta testing during February 2012.
